title: Oil Prices Rise on Yellen Rate Comments, Supply-Side Factors
text:
LONDONâ€”Oil prices rose on Friday as investors weighed comments by U.S. Federal Reserve Chairwoman Janet Yellen on a rate rise by year-end and supply-side developments in the market.
A weekly decline in U.S. oil stockpiles had boosted benchmark prices in the last session, and an indicator of oil drilling activity in the U.S. due later on Friday...
